Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋 随着轰的一声\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the beginning there was darkness... And then... BANG!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生了无限膨胀的时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Giving birth to an endless expanding existence of time, space and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所见超乎我们的想象 超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now see further than we've ever imagined, beyond the limits of our existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call... THE UNIVERSE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们的太阳系以外有行星吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are there planets beyond our solar system?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个问题很少有人敢探索\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a question few have dared to probe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上最初开始寻找行星的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The origin of hunting for planets started, really,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是些科学狂热份子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from the lunatic fringe of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在数百个神奇的星球已经被发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, hundreds of these exotic worlds have been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们中会有存在生命吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Could any of them be home to alien life?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前 我们发现这类行星是些…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right now, the sort of planets we're discovering are kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会立刻变为灰烬\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You would be incinerated immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前你真的有点对周围的环境感到兴奋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before you had a chance to really sort of groove on your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而有些行星还是很有希望\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But some planets hold more promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:01:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对格雷司43b星感到兴奋 几乎要跳起来了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm so excited about Gliese 436, I'm almost jumping out of my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们即将找到另外一颗地球了吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Could we be on the verge of finding another Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还是不知道我们的地球究竟是颗很普通的行星呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We still don't know whether our Earth is a commonly occurring planet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是十亿分之一的怪物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or a one-in-a-billion freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尖端的科学 陌生的星球 狂野的气候\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cutting-edge science, strange worlds, and wild weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴随着我们在宇宙中探寻"日外行星"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as we travel the Universe in search of"alien planets".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:24.00,Default,,0,0,1,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0}--==本影片由 {\1c&HFF8000&\b1}CMCT 团队{\fn华文楷体\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0} 荣誉出品==--\N更多精彩影视 请访问 {\fnCronos Pro Subhead\1c&HFF00FF&\b1}http://cmct.cc{\r}
